{"tid":2133440,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"殘破大亨注滿熱血 堅拒眼前由誰掠奪 日後歲月","createTime":"2020-07-31T05:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T06:14:09.000Z","uid":199804,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7df417091a675f01bef02951bdae22c9268bde50","tid":2133440,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T05:34:39.000Z","msg":"以初心 對抗暴政<br />\n不怕在選舉中氣喘 四眼無懼否決<br />\n理想長存 高空盤旋 從不缺<br />\n心裡梦 熱度總可 五區當選<br />\n<br />\n今天你為求獲勝<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG18dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=32376a74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網<br />\n鋪天蓋地永續了基本法 虛幻無形<br />\n封鎖我四眼然後隔絕四眼 恐怕我做法子<br />\n如何憑極地飛霜 凍結我四眼<br />\n我亦會重燃我這一套 五區當選"},{"pid":"167f367827048c9926502e41b062474363e47011","tid":2133440,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T05:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77daafdd1bb8cfed5617a4068c229ce274c04571","tid":2133440,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"梦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f038bb28ea6a50c68cc533a625472b34c612a39","tid":2133440,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T05:37:37.000Z","msg":"唔啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab2095ae92c3209b5d1c46d5ce49ec595fd9698","tid":2133440,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77daafdd1bb8cfed5617a4068c229ce274c04571","tid":2133440,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"梦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20